    "description": "反抗幸存者是一款奇幻风格的偏悠闲的Roguelike游戏，有两种游戏模式。<br><br>在两种模式中均有强化角色技能的系统，可以通过升级不同的技能强化角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122720/extras/4b360f26e34695ba54d20cc7bf919e29.avif?t=1726740070\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>反抗模式：在此模式中，玩家扮演召唤怪物的召唤师。<br><br>在游戏开始前需要选择6种怪物。在通关不同难度后，会陆续解锁新的怪物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122720/extras/f73ae1f149589810178f276711712bb8.avif?t=1726740070\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>游戏中通过召唤6种怪物与英雄战斗，在倒计时结束之前击败英雄则获得胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122720/extras/f76bea887488ecf2027ae25eb713b381.avif?t=1726740070\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>幸存模式：在此模式中，玩家扮演英雄。<br><br>在游戏开始前选择一位英雄。通关不同难度后，会陆续解锁新的英雄。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122720/extras/1bfd9a54a96b2d989480d41f7322b7fb.avif?t=1726740070\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>游戏中，英雄在怪物的攻势中存活至倒计时结束则获得胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122720/extras/3b959b0a081621fcb3a8200a49126487.avif?t=1726740070\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>以上就是游戏的大致玩法。",
